What does it mean for this to not be specified?

Can we ever have a PodGroup pull a template from some other type in the future?  Could that other type not need the name? 

Would it make sense to do something like:

```
type PodGroupTemplateReference struct {
    // one of the following must be set:
    Workload *WorkloadPodGroupTemplateReference
}

type WorkloadPodGroupTemplateReference struct {
    WorkloadName string
    PodGroupTemplateName string
}
```

